 War saw her face. "Do not think of this as a bad thing. Do what you want. 
Just bec drillbit proposed first does not mean a thing. Destructor was not 
around then. So how will you ever know. But all I can do is tell you this. 
Think of who makes you happy. Who you can see as your protector your love and 
your life. I know i cant help you make this desicion. No one can help you. I 
suggest you take some time away from both of them and think. Do not tell 
drillbit yet of what has happened for I fear what he may do. I leave you know 
to protecte destructor. I owe him that much. He is the noblest bot I have 
ever meet." He walked away and stood infront of the cr holding destructor 
standing guard.
